{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be corporate and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Ethereal Threads - Sustainable Fashion</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0d47a1; /* Deep Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #1976d2; /* Lighter Blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f5f5f5;\n            --footer-background: #1976d2;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 40px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 30px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            font-weight: 500;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #bbdefb; /* Very light blue for hover */\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 40px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: transparent;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 60px auto;\n            padding: 0 40px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section-title {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-weight: 700;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: left;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n        }\n\n        .about-content img {\n            max-width: 50%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .about-text h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .about-text p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-background);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            color: #bbdefb;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                padding: 20px;\n            }\n            nav ul {\n                margin-top: 15px;\n                flex-wrap: wrap;\n                justify-content: center;\n            }\n            nav ul li {\n                margin: 0 15px;\n            }\n            .hero {\n                padding: 60px 20px;\n            }\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            .container {\n                padding: 0 20px;\n            }\n            .about-content {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .about-content img {\n                max-width: 100%;\n                margin-bottom: 20px;\n            }\n            .section-title {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"logo\">Ethereal Threads</div>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#values\">Our Values</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Consciously Crafted. Beautifully Worn.</h1>\n        <p>Discover fashion that aligns with your style and your values. We believe in creating elegant, timeless pieces with the planet and people in mind.</p>\n        <a href=\"#collection\" class=\"cta-button\">Explore Our Collection</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"about\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">About Ethereal Threads</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/500x400/0d47a1/ffffff?text=Sustainable+Fabric\" alt=\"Sustainable fabric\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <h2>Our Commitment to Sustainability</h2>\n                <p>At Ethereal Threads, sustainability is woven into the fabric of our brand. We meticulously source eco-friendly materials, prioritize ethical manufacturing practices, and design durable, timeless pieces that transcend fleeting trends.</p>\n                <p>From organic cottons and recycled fibers to innovative plant-based textiles, every material is chosen for its minimal environmental impact and luxurious feel. Our production process emphasizes reduced water usage, lower energy consumption, and fair labor conditions.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"values\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">Our Core Values</h2>\n        <div class=\"features\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Ethical Production</h3>\n                <p>We partner with factories that ensure fair wages, safe working conditions, and respect for all workers.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Eco-Friendly Materials</h3>\n                <p>Utilizing organic, recycled, and biodegradable fabrics to minimize our ecological footprint.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Timeless Design</h3>\n                <p>Creating versatile, enduring styles that you'll love and wear for years to come.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <h3>Transparency</h3>\n                <p>Providing clear information about our supply chain and manufacturing processes.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container\" id=\"contact\">\n        <h2 class=\"section-title\">Get In Touch</h2>\n        <p>Have questions or want to learn more about our sustainable practices? We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n        <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:info@etherealthreads.com\">info@etherealthreads.com</a></p>\n        <p>Follow us on social media: <a href=\"#\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"#\">Facebook</a></p>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Ethereal Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Committed to a sustainable future for fashion.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}